description:
RiPort table:  Radio interface port configuration data.

- dateTime: Timestamp of data recording.
- Area_Name: Geographic location of the radio cell.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant Cell ID.
- Id3: Field Replaceable Unit (FRU) identifier.
- Id4:  Data identifier, likely related to SFP module.
- vsDataType: Data type identifier.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- RiPort.transmissionStandard: Transmission standard used (e.g., Ethernet, CPRI).
- RiPort.administrativeState: Administrative state of the port (e.g., unlocked).
- RiPort.sfpModuleRef: Reference to the SFP module.
- RiPort.riPortId: Unique identifier of the radio interface port.
- RiPort.channelRef: Reference to the specific channel within the SFP module.
- RiPort.preferredSfpProductNumber: Preferred SFP product number.
